Founding Partners

Ways to
Give
When you give, you bring the gift of play to kids and adults with disabilities.
That’s because your support could fund need-based scholarships for people with disabilities both young and old to ensure they can participate in sports or social activities both sponsored by the Space Coast Field of Dreams or other organization members who need our help. Your gift could also provide funding for adaptive equipment that creates a safer, more inclusive experience for those playing sports, on the playground or trying to dance the night away. Know that when you give, however we can help children and kids at heart who simply want to play, that’s the way you’re going to make an impact at the Space Coast Field of Dreams.
There are multiple ways you can support our mission:
Use your credit card to give today.
Make a Donation
